				<h2>A simple credit ledger smart contract</h2>
				<p>Credit coin allows you to extend a provable credit line to your vendors and service providers. Credit coin is a liability balance with a repayment plan built into the coin. </p>
				
			</header>

		<p>As a Lender - Create a foolproof way to lend money with a provable credit and trackable repayment.<br/>
		As a Project Manager - Create a corpus plan with vendor/service provider credit which can will be recovered authomatically.<br/> 
		As a borrower - Accept credit and maintain a planned repayment schedule</p>

